short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 一个浏览器标签页管理工具（A browser tab management tool）

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: 如果你在浏览器打开了很多标签页，每次想找到某个标签页时，会很难找到。此工具可以以列表的形式帮你管理所有标签页，帮你快速找到并进入你想要的标签页。（If you have many tabs open in your browser, it will be difficult to find a particular tab every time you want to find it. This tool can help you manage all tabs in the form of a list, and help you quickly find and enter the tabs you want.）
